12 operations for persons engaging in poultry feeding operations, and,
13 if such review, inspection, or investigation results in the finding
14 of a violation of the provisions of Section 20-61 of Title 2 of the
15 Oklahoma Statutes, the Department shall revoke the license of such
16 individuals engaging in the poultry feeding operation pursuant to
17 Section 20-61 of Title 2 of the Oklahoma Statutes. The Department
18 shall not reissue a license for any operation whose license was
19 revoked pursuant to this subsection.
20 C. The Department shall promulgate any rules necessary to
21 implement the provisions of this section.
22 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
